latestIgtvVideos.caption:
SOUND ON❗️Content creation is hard. Whoever said otherwise is a liar!! 
I put so much attention to detail in this series that I was on a verge of quitting. If it wasn't for my family I would've given up on this. From holding the blow dryer, filming to get the perfect shot, holding lights, draping the clothes, staying up at odd hours, they did it all. This post is just a to show you guys that there's a lot of hard work, dedication and struggles that goes behind the scenes. So when you see a good piece of content that you actually like, please engage. Don't do passive consumption of a content you like and lastly THANK YOU FOR ALL THE LOVE ON THIS SERIES. 
.
.
.
.
